lyrics:
[Verse]
In this Canadian town, the snow starts to fall
As winter's enchantment embraces us all
Indie rock melodies blend with the breeze
Dream pop harmonies dance through the trees

[Chorus]
Mesmerizing winter, oh, how you captivate
With your icy whispers and magical fate
Tropical funk grooves melt away the cold
As we embrace the music that winter unfolds
